OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,F57-year-old Antonio De Lemos works
OL,7,Fwith John and added: "For someone to
OL,8,Fretire in this island, the old age
OL,9,Fpension should be minimum, for a
OL,10,Fsingle guy, #500 a week - #1,000 for a
OL,11,Fcouple. Then they can afford to
OL,12,Fretire."
OL,14,FThe state pension age has risen to 67
OL,15,Fin Jersey and 70 in Guernsey.
