OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,FBen Shenton, Chair of Age Concern
OL,7,FJersey, told ITV News: "In Jersey,
OL,8,Fyou've got a two-tier pension; those
OL,9,Fwith the private pensions that can
OL,10,Fafford to retire, these are public
OL,11,Fsector workers and people that work in
OL,12,Ffinance.
OL,14,F"Then you have people who don't have
OL,15,Fprivate pensions and these tend to be
OL,16,Fthe lower paid and, quite honestly,
OL,17,Fwith the high cost of rent and living
OL,18,Fin Jersey, they're forced to work much
OL,19,Flater in life
