OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,FHe added: "A few people do have jobs
OL,7,Fthat they love and choose to work on,
OL,8,Fbut I think the majority look forward
OL,9,Fto their retirement.
OL,11,F"If they don't have a private pension,
OL,12,Fthey'll look at what the state pension
OL,13,Fgives them and think, 'I can't exist
OL,14,Fon this, I'm going to have to carry on
OL,15,Fworking."
OL,17,FKeith Bienvenu has been working at
OL,18,FForest Stores in Guernsey since 1961
OL,19,Fand continues working not for money,
OL,20,Fbut because he enjoys it.
