OL,6,FHe said: "I think it's probably
OL,7,Fbecause I still enjoy it and being my
OL,8,Fboss I can pick my hours and I am free
OL,9,Fto come and go as I need.
OL,11,F"Jobs like this, you're meeting people
OL,12,Fall the time which is part of the joy
OL,13,Fof the job."
OL,15,FIn response, Jersey's government said:
OL,16,F"Not every employer in Jersey offers
OL,17,Fan occupational pension and a project
OL,18,Fis underway to address that gap and
OL,19,Fallow all workers to save for their
OL,20,Fown retirement.
