OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,F"In addition to the States Old Age
OL,7,FPension (OAP), lower-income pensioners
OL,8,Fmay be eligible for additional
OL,9,Fgovernment support measures.
OL,11,F"These include Pension Plus and the
OL,12,FHealth Access Scheme, for medical
OL,13,Fcosts and GP services; the Cold
OL,14,FWeather Bonus; the Christmas Bonus;
OL,15,Fthe Community Costs Bonus, to help
OL,16,Fwith the cost of living; and free TV
OL,17,Flicenses.
