OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,F"Pensioners who think they may be
OL,7,Feligible and are not currently
OL,8,Freceiving these benefits should
OL,9,Fcontact the Pensions and Care Team."
OL,11,F"Since taking office the Social
OL,12,FSecurity Minister has prioritised
OL,13,Fmeeting with key stakeholders such as
OL,14,FAge Concern to discuss how the cost of
OL,15,Fliving pressures can be addressed. She
OL,16,Fwill also meet with the Older Persons
OL,17,FLiving Forum at the earliest
OL,18,Fopportunity."
