OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,FDeputy Peter Roffey, President of
OL,7,FGuernsey's Committee for Employment
OL,8,Fand Social Security, added: "Each year
OL,9,Fthe States increases its pension in
OL,10,Fline with guideline policy.
OL,12,F"The current policy ensures that the
OL,13,FStates' pension is always increased at
OL,14,Fthe rate of inflation, as a minimum.
OL,15,FOn top of that the pension goes up
OL,16,Ffurther by a third of the difference
OL,17,Fbetween inflation and the increase in
OL,18,Faverage earnings during those periods
OL,19,Fwhen wages are rising faster than
OL,20,Fprices."
