OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,FDeputy Roffey added: "Despite this, we
OL,7,Fknow there are circumstances where the
OL,8,FStates' pension alone may not be
OL,9,Fenough to live on. If pensioners are
OL,10,Fconcerned that their income is not
OL,11,Fenough, I encourage them to contact
OL,12,FSocial Security to enquire about
OL,13,FIncome Support.
OL,15,F"This includes support with medical
OL,16,Fcosts, a Winter Fuel Allowance, and an
OL,17,FExtra Needs Allowance. Other support
OL,18,Fis also available for people who fall
OL,19,Fjust outside of the Income Support
OL,20,Frequirement.
