OL,3,CChannel Islanders delaying retirement
OL,4,C"as state pension is not enough alone"
OL,6,F"To help future pensioners enjoy a
OL,7,Fmore comfortable lifestyle, and to
OL,8,Freduce the demand on tax-funded income
OL,9,Fsupport, the States has approved
OL,10,Fsecondary pensions legislation which
OL,11,Fwill provide islanders with the
OL,12,Fopportunity to save more now for their
OL,13,Fretirement.
OL,15,F"These savings will be tax deductible,
OL,16,Fand employers will contribute.
OL,18,F"From 1st July 2024, larger employers
OL,19,F(those with 26+ employers) will be
OL,20,Frequired to enrol their employees into
OL,21,Fan approved secondary pension.
